[playful music]

00:43.244 --> 00:46.847
*

00:46.880 --> 00:50.451
- HEY.

00:54.655 --> 00:56.257
- WHOA-HO!

00:56.290 --> 00:57.391
- OH, NO!

00:57.425 --> 01:00.161
WHAT IS THAT ABOUT?

01:00.194 --> 01:04.332
I GOT THIS.
- I GOT IT, I GOT IT.

01:08.136 --> 01:13.073
[indistinct chatter]

01:15.609 --> 01:17.578
BUT I KNEW WHAT IT MEANT.
- YEAH.

01:17.611 --> 01:19.180
- THERE YOU GO, SIR.
- OH...

01:19.213 --> 01:20.314
I'LL GET THAT.

01:20.348 --> 01:23.551
- NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

01:44.372 --> 01:45.839
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

01:45.873 --> 01:49.343
I GOT IT.

01:49.377 --> 01:52.246
THANK YOU.

01:52.280 --> 01:55.216
[whistling]

02:01.655 --> 02:02.723
- $13.50.

02:02.756 --> 02:04.725
- MICHAEL, NO, NO, NO.

02:04.758 --> 02:07.195
- NO, I GOT THIS.
- MICHAEL!

02:07.228 --> 02:09.197
- NO!
- THANK YOU.

02:09.230 --> 02:11.165
COME ON.

02:20.274 --> 02:22.376
OH, I GOT IT.

02:22.410 --> 02:23.777
UNLESS YOU WANT
ANYTHING ELSE.

02:23.811 --> 02:26.214
- YEAH, I DO.
- DESSERT?

02:26.247 --> 02:27.348
GOOD BOY.

02:27.381 --> 02:29.517
CHOCOLATE DEATH, TWO FORKS.

02:29.550 --> 02:30.918
- I DON'T WANT DESSERT.

02:30.951 --> 02:32.553
- OH.

02:32.586 --> 02:35.389
ONE FORK.

02:35.423 --> 02:37.525
- I WANT YOU TO STOP PAYING
FOR EVERYTHING.

02:37.558 --> 02:39.660
- I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.
- YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

02:39.693 --> 02:41.395
YOU'RE ALWAYS PICKING UP
THE CHECK,

02:41.429 --> 02:43.297
YOU'RE BUYING THE MOVIE TICKETS
AND GETTING THE GROCERIES.

02:43.331 --> 02:45.233
- SO?

02:45.266 --> 02:47.401
- SO I'M WORKING.
YOU DON'T HAVE TO SUPPORT ME.

02:47.435 --> 02:49.570
- I CAN AFFORD IT. YOU CAN'T.
WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?

02:49.603 --> 02:51.972
- IT'S A BIG DEAL TO ME.

02:52.005 --> 02:54.542
- I LIKE TO TAKE YOU
NICE PLACES, MICHAEL.

02:54.575 --> 02:56.910
- AND I LIKE TO GO TO THEM,
BUT...

02:56.944 --> 02:59.447
I DON'T LIKE YOU PAYING FOR ME
ALL THE TIME.

02:59.480 --> 03:03.517
I-I FEEL...FUNNY.

03:03.551 --> 03:06.687
- YOU PAY WHEN YOU CAN,
DON'T YOU?

03:06.720 --> 03:10.724
- YEAH, AND SPEAKING
OF WHICH...

03:10.758 --> 03:14.295
THIS MONTH'S HOUSE EXPENSES.

03:14.328 --> 03:16.364
- THANK YOU.

03:16.397 --> 03:18.832
SEE? I'M TAKING YOUR MONEY.
- YEAH.

03:18.866 --> 03:20.401
$300 A MONTH.

03:20.434 --> 03:21.635
YOU SURE THAT'S HALF
OF EVERYTHING?

03:21.669 --> 03:24.705
- SURE.

03:24.738 --> 03:27.241
- THE CLEANING LADY?
THE UTILITIES?

03:27.275 --> 03:29.209
- CHOCOLATE DEATH!

03:35.316 --> 03:36.850
YOU WANT A BITE?

03:44.558 --> 03:47.528
[dance music]

03:47.561 --> 03:55.503
*

04:07.315 --> 04:10.784
- * YOU GOT CAUGHT RED-HANDED

04:10.818 --> 04:14.488
* AND REACHING

04:14.522 --> 04:19.393
* INTO SOMEONE ELSE'S
LITTLE COOKIE JAR *

04:22.363 --> 04:23.897
- ISN'T DYKE NIGHT FUN?

04:23.931 --> 04:27.335
- CAN'T REMEMBER
WHEN I HAD SUCH A GOOD TIME.

04:27.368 --> 04:28.902
- I HATE DYKE NIGHT.

04:28.936 --> 04:32.473
- ME TOO.
I FEEL SO VIOLATED.

04:32.506 --> 04:34.542
- * I'M GONNA FIND OUT
JUST HOW RECKLESS YOU ARE *

04:37.611 --> 04:40.648
* YOU THINK
I'LL STAY FOREVER *

04:40.681 --> 04:44.652
- EWW.
WHAT ARE THEY DOING?

04:44.685 --> 04:47.655
- * SOMEDAY YOUR EYES
WILL FINALLY SEE *

04:47.688 --> 04:51.024
- THE "MUNCHER MASH"?
I DON'T KNOW.

04:51.058 --> 04:52.560
- SO, MEL,

04:52.593 --> 04:55.095
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU WERE AT DYKE NIGHT?

04:55.128 --> 04:57.765
- OH, BEFORE I MET LINDSAY.

04:57.798 --> 05:01.669
- REMEMBER, WE WEREN'T GOING
TO MENTION HER.

05:01.702 --> 05:03.036
- HEY.

05:03.070 --> 05:05.939
SHE'S CUTE.

05:05.973 --> 05:10.411
- SHE REMINDS ME OF LINDSAY
WITH RED HAIR.

05:10.444 --> 05:15.583
- WHAT ABOUT HER?

05:15.616 --> 05:21.555
- SHE REMINDS ME OF LINDSAY
WITH BLACK HAIR.

05:21.589 --> 05:22.823
- DON'T TELL ME.

05:22.856 --> 05:27.094
HE REMINDS YOU OF LINDSAY
IN DRAG.

05:27.127 --> 05:29.497
- I CAN'T HELP IT.
I MISS HER.

05:29.530 --> 05:31.965
I THOUGHT
WE'D BE TOGETHER FOREVER,

05:31.999 --> 05:33.634
THAT SHE'D BE
THE ONE I KISSED GOOD NIGHT

05:33.667 --> 05:36.136
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

05:36.169 --> 05:37.771
NOW I LIVE
WITH MY COUSIN RITA

05:37.805 --> 05:39.106
AND KISS HER GOOD NIGHT.

05:39.139 --> 05:40.808
CHRIST!

05:40.841 --> 05:44.144
- [sighing]
LOOK, MEL,

05:44.177 --> 05:45.913
IT'S BEEN GREAT HANGING
WITH YOU.

05:45.946 --> 05:48.849
YOU'VE BEEN A GREAT FAG-HAG.

05:48.882 --> 05:50.884
- ONLY THE THING IS

05:50.918 --> 05:52.886
FAG-HAGS ARE SUPPOSED
TO BE FUN.

05:52.920 --> 05:56.524
- SO WHY DON'T YOU
GO SEE LINDSAY?

05:56.557 --> 05:58.726
TELL HER HOW YOU FEEL

05:58.759 --> 06:00.561
AND MAKE UP WITH HER, OKAY?

06:00.594 --> 06:03.531
- HOW CAN I DO THAT
AFTER WHAT I DID?

06:03.564 --> 06:06.467
- WHATEVER YOU DID, YOU KNOW,
IT TAKES TWO.

06:06.500 --> 06:08.135
YOU GOT NOTHING TO LOSE,

06:08.168 --> 06:11.104
UNLESS YOU REALLY WANT
TO WAIT AROUND FOR THE NEXT...

06:11.138 --> 06:13.474
DYKE NIGHT.
- BRRRR.

06:28.021 --> 06:30.824
- [sighs]

06:44.705 --> 06:46.907
- YOU DRINK TOO MUCH COFFEE.

06:46.940 --> 06:48.776
- THIS ISN'T COFFEE.
IT'S LATTE.

06:48.809 --> 06:50.844
- IT'S JUST COFFEE
THAT COSTS 5 BUCKS.

06:50.878 --> 06:53.046
AND IT STILL
CAUSES HIGH BLOOD PRESSURE,

06:53.080 --> 06:56.016
HEART ATTACK,
POOR SEXUAL PERFORMANCE.

06:56.049 --> 06:57.618
- I HAVEN'T HAD
ANY COMPLAINTS.

06:57.651 --> 06:59.219
- NOT TO MENTION INSOMNIA.

06:59.252 --> 07:01.188
- WELL, USUALLY
WHEN I'M IN MY BED,

07:01.221 --> 07:03.090
I'M NOT ASLEEP ANYWAY,
SO IT REALLY DOESN'T MATTER.

07:03.123 --> 07:04.592
- [laughing]

07:04.625 --> 07:07.160
SEE, FORTUNATELY
I HAVE YOUTH ON MY SIDE.

07:07.194 --> 07:09.162
I CAN STAY UP ALL NIGHT
FUCKING

07:09.196 --> 07:12.666
AND STILL SCORE 1,500
ON MY S.A.T.s.

07:12.700 --> 07:14.034
- 1,500?

07:14.067 --> 07:15.536
- YEP.

07:15.569 --> 07:17.471
- WOW, YOU COULD GET
INTO ANY SCHOOL YOU WANTED

07:17.505 --> 07:19.507
WITH A SCORE LIKE THAT.

07:19.540 --> 07:21.809
- I APPLIED TO DARTMOUTH,
BROWN--

07:21.842 --> 07:24.612
- YOU'RE GOING OUT OF STATE?

07:24.645 --> 07:27.481
- WHY? DO YOU GIVE A SHIT?

07:27.515 --> 07:30.751
- IT'S JUST THE FIRST
I'VE HEARD OF IT, THAT'S ALL.

07:30.784 --> 07:33.587
- YOU DO!

07:33.621 --> 07:36.690
YOU GIVE A SHIT!

07:36.724 --> 07:39.226
YOU GIVE A SHIT!

07:39.259 --> 07:42.630
